snippet.title: Tears of Themis Closed Beta Registration has begun! First Official PV(JP Dubbing Version) Launched!
snippet.description:
❤ Register now to experience the game before the official release: https://tot.mihoyo.com/CBTsign-up/

❤ JP CV info:
